        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 72654,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Hasta ahora hemos aprendido cómo crear un bucle <code>while</code>, ahora enfoquémonos en cómo detenerlos para que no se repitan infinitamente.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Creating the variable",
            "id": 72642,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para detener un bucle, comenzamos creando una variable fuera del bucle.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"13\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"20\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>let</code> seguido de <code>keepGoing</code> y luego <code>=</code>, <code>true</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Variable in the condition",
            "id": 72644,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Usamos la variable en la condición para decidir si el bucle debe ejecutar su bloque de código o no. Por ejemplo, <code>(keepGoing === true)</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (keepGoing === \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"38\" /><option startIndex=\"39\" endIndex=\"42\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>keepGoing</code> seguido de <code>===</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Updating the variable",
            "id": 72650,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Dentro del bloque de código, detenemos el bucle estableciendo <code>keepGoing</code> a <code>false</code> para que la condición devuelva <code>false</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (keepGoing === \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"91\" endIndex=\"96\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>false</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Stopping the loop",
            "id": 72655,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>El bucle ejecuta todo su bloque de código porque <code>keepGoing</code> es <code>true</code> al principio, pero no se ejecuta de nuevo si establecemos <code>keepGoing</code> a <code>false</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (keepGoing === \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;keepGoing: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + keepGoing);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;keepGoing: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + keepGoing);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"105\" endIndex=\"110\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"keepGoing: true\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"keepGoing: false\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>false</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Creating the variable",
            "id": 72718,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cómo sabemos que este bucle se ejecuta y nunca deja de repetir su bloque de código?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isLoading = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Loading Game&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Loading Game\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loading Game\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loading Game\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">No hay ninguna variable en la condición</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Este bucle no se ejecutará ya que la condición es <code>false</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">No hay ninguna variable en la condición.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Variable in the condition",
            "id": 72719,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cómo sabemos que el bucle <code>while</code> omite su bloque de código?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isLoading = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (isLoading === \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Loading Game&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">El valor de <code>isLoading</code> es <code>false</code> pero la condición está verificando si es <code>true</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">El valor de <code>isLoading</code> es <code>false</code> y la condición está verificando si es <code>false</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">El valor de <code>isLoading</code> es <code>false</code> pero la condición está verificando si es <code>true</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
