            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cómo sabemos que este bucle se detiene?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (keepGoing === \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Just keep swimming&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Just keep swimming\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">La variable <code>keepGoing</code> se actualiza a <code>false</code> dentro del bloque de código</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">No sabemos si el bucle se detiene</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">La variable <code>keepGoing</code> se actualiza a <code>false</code> dentro del bloque de código.</p></body></html>"
          },
