            "title": "Example: Creating the variable",
            "id": 72723,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para usar la variable en la condición del bucle while, créala fuera del bloque de código.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (keepPlaying === \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Now Playing: Ryan Paris&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Now Playing: Ryan Paris\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>let</code> seguido de <code>keepPlaying</code> y luego <code>=</code>, <code>true</code>, <code>;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
